title: Lenny Breau - Cabin Fever - 1997 [flac]
description:
Lenny Breau - Cabin Fever - 1997 [flac]

A full album of just Lenny and his guitar, with little or no post production. Quiet, delicate, even sombre at times, apparently recorded (exact date unknown but probably 1975) when he was grieving for his late father.
